    "(62)The inequality in this specific form is adapted from Zeng et al. [2022][Lemma 4].Combining ( 61) with ( 62) leads toE[J f (π θ k, ϕ ω k+1, μk+1) -J f (π θ k+1, ϕ ω k+1, μk+1)] ≤ - α k 16 E[∥∇ θ J f (π θ k, ϕ ω k, μk)∥ 2] + 2L 2 V α k E[ε V f,k] + 3L 2 V ξ 2 k + 2B F (B D + B H)α k ξ k - 3(1 -γ)τ ρ 2 min p 2 min α k 8|S| J f (π ⋆ (ϕ ω k, μk), ϕ ω k, μk) -J f (π θ k, ϕ ω k, μk) ≤ - α k 16 E[∥∇ θ J f (π θ k, ϕ ω k, μk)∥ 2] + 2L 2 V α k E[ε V f,k] + 3L 2 V ξ 2 k + 2B F (B D + B H)α k ξ k - 3(1 -γ)τ 2 ρ 3 min p 2 min α k 8|S| ∥π ⋆ (ϕ ω k, μk) -π θ k ∥ 2.",
    "(63)where the last inequality follows from (56).Within this subsection, we denote x k = (ϕ ω k, μk).",
    "Due to the L V -smoothness of the function J f, we haveJ f (π θ k, ϕ ω k, μk) -J f (π θ k, ϕ ω k+1, μk+1) ≤ -⟨∇ x J f (π θ k, ϕ ω k, μk), x k+1 -x k ⟩ + L V 2 ∥x k+1 -x k ∥ 2 = -⟨∇ x J f (π θ k, ϕ ω k, μk) -∇ x J f (π, ϕ ω k, μk) | π=π ⋆ (ϕω k,μ k), x k+1 -x k ⟩ + L V 2 ∥x k+1 -x k ∥ 2 -⟨∇ x J f (π, ϕ ω k, μk) | π=π ⋆ (ϕω k,μ k), x k+1 -x k ⟩ = -⟨∇ x J f (π θ k, ϕ ω k, μk) -∇ x J f (π, ϕ ω k, μk) | π=π ⋆ (ϕω k,μ k), x k+1 -x k ⟩ + L V 2 ∥x k+1 -x k ∥ 2 -⟨∇ x J f (π ⋆ (ϕ ω k, μk), ϕ ω k, μk), x k+1 -x k ⟩ ≤ -⟨∇ x J f (π θ k, ϕ ω k, μk) -∇ x J f (π, ϕ ω k, μk) | π=π ⋆ (ϕω k,μ k), x k+1 -x k ⟩ + L V 2 ∥x k+1 -x k ∥ 2 + J f (π ⋆ (ϕ ω k, μk), ϕ ω k, μk) -J f (π ⋆ (ϕ ω k+1, μk+1), ϕ ω k+1, μk+1) + L V 2 ∥x k+1 -x k ∥ 2,where the second inequality follows from the fact that for an L-smooth function f: R d → R we have f (x) -f (y) ≥ -⟨∇f (x), y -x⟩ -L 2 ∥y -x∥ 2.",
    "The second equations above uses the relationship ∇x J f (π ⋆ (ϕ ω k, μk), ϕ ω k, μk) = ∇ x J f (π, ϕ ω k, μk) | π=π ⋆ (ϕω k,μ k), which holds as the partial gradient with respect to π is zero at the optimizer (under entropy regularization τ > 0, the policy π ⋆ (ϕ, µ) is in the interior of the probability simplex for any ϕ, µ), i.e.∂J f (π ⋆ (ϕ ω k, μk), ϕ ω k, μk) ∂π ⋆ (ϕ ω k, μk) = 0.Taking the expectation and plugging in the result from Lemma 6,E[J f (π θ k, ϕ ω k, μk) -J f (π θ k, ϕ ω k+1, μk+1)] ≤ (1 -γ)τ 2 ρ 3 min p 2 min α k 4|S| E[∥π ⋆ (ϕ ω k, μk) -π θ k ∥ 2] + 2|S|L 2 V L 2 D L 2 H ξ 2 k (1 -γ)τ 2 ρ 3 min p 2 min α k E[∥π ⋆ (ϕ ω k,μ k) -π θ k ∥ 2] + 2|S|L 2 V η 2 2 ζ 2 k (1 -γ)τ 2 ρ 3 min p 2 min α k E[ε ϕ k] + 16|S|L 2 L 4 V L 2 D L 2 H ξ 2 k (1 -γ)τ 2 ρ 3 min p 2 min α k E[ε µ k] + 8|S|L 2 V ζ 2 k (1 -γ)τ 2 ρ 3 min p 2 min α k E[ε V l,k] + J f (π ⋆ (ϕ ω k, μk), ϕ ω k, μk) -J f (π ⋆ (ϕ ω k+1, μk+1), ϕ ω k+1, μk+1) + L V E[∥x k+1 -x k ∥ 2].",
